---
import BentoItem from './BentoItem.astro'
---

<section
  class={`w-full max-w-[1400px] grid grid-cols-10 auto-rows-[30rem] gap-4 mx-auto p-20`}
>
  <BentoItem
    class="col-span-10 md:col-span-4"
    title="ANDORRA: EL CENIT DE LOS PREMIOS ESLAND"
  >
    <div
      slot="image"
      class="-z-10 absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 h-full w-full group-hover:scale-110 bg-blue-950 transition-scale duration-1000 bg-blend-luminosity ease-in-out opacity-90 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat"
      style="background-image: url('/mountain.webp')"
    >
    </div>
    <p slot="content" class="max-w-xl">
      Este año, el momento de la alfombra azul será sustituido y mejorado,
      gracias a los increíbles paisajes andorranos, por una <strong>
        alfombra blanca en plena nieve</strong
      >, situada en las <strong>pistas de esquí de Andorra</strong>.
    </p>
  </BentoItem>
  <BentoItem
    class="col-span-10 md:col-span-6"
    title=" LA ALFOMBRA BLANCA"
    subtitle="16 de febrero de 2024"
  >
    <div
      slot="image"
      class="-z-10 absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 h-full w-full group-hover:scale-110 bg-blue-950 transition-scale duration-1000 bg-blend-luminosity ease-in-out opacity-90 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat"
      style="background-image: url('/mountain.webp')"
    >
    </div>
  </BentoItem>
  <BentoItem
    class="col-span-10 md:col-span-6"
    title="LA GALA"
    subtitle="17 de febrero 2024"
  >
    <div
      slot="image"
      class="-z-10 absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 h-full w-full group-hover:scale-110 bg-blue-950 transition-scale duration-1000 bg-blend-luminosity ease-in-out opacity-90 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat"
      style="background-image: url('/mountain.webp')"
    >
    </div>
  </BentoItem>
  <BentoItem
    class="col-span-10 md:col-span-4"
    title="DISFRUTA DEL REDDIT DE LA COMUNIDAD"
  >
    <div
      slot="image"
      class="-z-10 absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 h-full w-full group-hover:scale-110 bg-blue-950 transition-scale duration-1000 bg-blend-luminosity ease-in-out opacity-90 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat"
      style="background-image: url('/mountain.webp')"
    >
    </div>
  </BentoItem>
</section>
